NON SIGNIFICANT CHANGES

    o Bux fix in annovartomaf.
    o Rainfall plot improvement - Better handling of empty contigs.
    o Better parsing of HGVSp annotations.
    o Default value for useAll in read.maf changed from FALSE to TRUE.
    o FLAG notes
    o Added CITATION file.

