CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.33
-------------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o icgcSimpleMutationToMAF - convert ICGC Simpale Somatic Mutation Format to MAF

SIGNIFICANT USER-LEVEL CHANGES

    o Now read.maf validates MAF for repeated variants mapping to multiple transcripts of same gene.

NON SIGNIFICANT CHANGES

